      "meta_description": "",
      "relevant_text_blocks": [
        "Survival Saga is a challenge event in Last Z where you take on different tasks for rewards. In each challenge, you’ll have to defeat a specific zombie at a certain level on the “World Map.”",
        "The event lasts for 3 days, and you can pick between two difficulty modes: Normal and Advanced. Normal mode has 9 levels, while Advanced has 6.",
        "As you move up in difficulty, the zombies you face get tougher. So, it’s a good idea to team up with your alliance members to make it easier to take them down!",
        "When the event starts, players have to pick a difficulty level. Once you choose, you can’t change it for that round.",
        "To move on to the next difficulty, you need to complete all the challenges in the current level.",
        "The rewards in this event are split into two types: difficulty completion rewards and milestone rewards for each difficulty level.",
        "Here’s a table that shows the recommended power and rewards you can get based on the difficulty level.",
        "Here are the pictures of milestone rewards in this event.",
